{"tid":2401302,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發覺輕小說好鐘意將金幣對照金額 但完全無意義？","createTime":"2021-02-09T15:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T12:22:24.000Z","uid":82450,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"998a3c43a04966f26fc1d3eadc2046a07c38c468","tid":2401302,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"例如<br />\n1銅幣=10(單位)<br />\n1銀幣=100<br />\n1金=1000<br />\n1白金=10000<br />\n<br />\n但平時買嘢係就咁幾銅幾銀做訂價，完全無需要用到後面個金額單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係有時候無啦啦做啲任/拎獎勵就用金額寫，之後呃字數話姐係代表幾多金幾多銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇個陣完全skip咗唔理個段，但又老是常出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d3417bff29ce3c7990eb8f35b95872b48d5fa3","tid":2401302,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"懶係有貨幣系統，襯托異世界技術落後，你咁講真係幾冇意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3fa93f02578287ab21a56ae5975a453232f4240","tid":2401302,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:21:23.000Z","msg":"動物台難得高質po"},{"pid":"cb0dfe0f0e80051d6de60d52d1eabfa75e4583ce","tid":2401302,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81d3417bff29ce3c7990eb8f35b95872b48d5fa3","tid":2401302,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"懶係有貨幣系統，襯托異世界技術落後，你咁講真係幾冇意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"我係因為個啲作品多數都係一下掙大錢永遠都使唔曬，但又成日講金額對照計婆仔數，覺得好奇怪"},{"pid":"38643ccc3c6948a15e315b4d77c2bf5f71769b94","tid":2401302,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb0dfe0f0e80051d6de60d52d1eabfa75e4583ce","tid":2401302,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81d3417bff29ce3c7990eb8f35b95872b48d5fa3","tid":2401302,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,